 earth."}, {:version=>"Berean Study Bible", :text=>"Then God said to Noah, “The end of all living creatures has come before Me, because through them the earth is full of violence. Now behold, I will destroy both them and the earth."}, {:version=>"New American Standard Bible ", :text=>"Then God said to Noah, \"The end of all flesh has come before Me; for the earth is filled with violence because of them; and behold, I am about to destroy them with the earth."}, {:version=>"New King James Version", :text=>"And God said to Noah, “The end of all flesh has come before Me, for the earth is filled with violence through them; and behold, I will destroy them with the earth."}, {:version=>"King James Bible", :text=>"And God said unto Noah, The end of all flesh is come before me; for the earth is filled with violence through them; and, behold, I will destroy them with the earth."}, {:version=>"Christian Standard Bible", :text=>"Then God said to Noah, \"I have decided to put an end to every creature, for the earth is filled with wickedness because of them; therefore I am going to destroy them along with the earth."}, {:version=>"Contemporary English Version", :text=>"So he told Noah: Cruelty and violence have spread everywhere. Now I'm going to destroy the whole earth and all its people. "}, {:version=>"Good News Translation", :text=>"God said to Noah, \"I have decided to put an end to all people. I will destroy them completely, because the world is full of their violent deeds. "}, {:version=>"Holman Christian Standard Bible", :text=>"Then God said to Noah, \"I have decided to put an end to every creature, for the earth is filled with wickedness because of them; therefore I am going to destroy them along with the earth.\" "}, {:version=>"International Standard Version", :text=>"So God announced to Noah, \"I've decided to destroy every living thing on earth, because it has become filled with violence due to them. Look! I'm about to annihilate them, along with the earth. "}, {:version=>"NET Bible", :text=>"So God said to Noah, \"I have decided that all living creatures must die, for the earth is filled with violence because of them. Now I am about to destroy them and the earth."}, {:version=>"New Heart English Bible", :text=>"And God said to Noah, \"The end of all flesh has come before me, for the earth is filled with violence through them. And look, I will destroy them with the earth. "}, {:version=>"GOD'S WORD® Translation", :text=>"God said to Noah, \"I have decided to put an end to all people because the earth is full of their violence. Now I'm going to destroy them along with the earth."}, {:version=>"JPS Tanakh 1917", :text=>"And God said unto Noah: 'The end of all flesh is come before Me; for the earth is filled with violence through them; and, behold, I will destroy them with the earth."}, {:version=>"New American Standard 1977 ", :text=>"Then God said to Noah, “The end of all flesh has come before Me; for the earth is filled with violence because of them; and behold, I am about to destroy them with the earth."}, {:version=>"King James 2000 Bible", :text=>"And God said unto Noah, The end of all flesh is come before me; for the earth is filled with violence through them; and, behold, I will destroy them with the earth."}, {:version=>"American King James Version", :text=>"And God said to Noah, The end of all flesh is come before me; for the earth is filled with violence through them; and, behold, I will destroy them with the earth."}, {:version=>"American Standard Version", :text=>"And God said unto Noah, The end of all flesh is come before me; for the earth is filled with violence through them; and, behold, I will destroy them with the earth."}, {:version=>"Brenton Septuagint Translation", :text=>"And the Lord God said to Noe, A period of all men is come before me; because the earth has been filled with iniquity by them, and, behold, I destroy them and the earth."}, {:version=>"Douay-Rheims Bible", :text=>"He said to Noe: The end of all flesh is come before me, the earth is filled with iniquity through them, and I will destroy them with the earth. "}, {:version=>"Darby Bible Translation", :text=>"And God said to Noah, The end of all flesh is come before me, for the earth is full of violence through them; and behold, I will destroy them with the earth."}, {:version=>"English Revised Version", :text=>"And God said unto Noah, The end of all flesh is come before me; for the earth is filled with violence through them; and, behold, I will destroy them with the earth."}, {:version=>"Webster's Bible Translation", :text=>"And God said to Noah, The end of all flesh is come before me; for the earth is filled with violence through them: and behold, I will destroy them with the earth."}, {:version=>"World English Bible", :text=>"God said to Noah, \"The end of all flesh has come before me, for the earth is filled with violence through them. Behold, I will destroy them with the earth."}, {:version=>"Young's Literal Translation", :text=>" And God said to Noah, 'An end of all flesh hath come before Me, for the earth hath been full of violence from their presence; and lo, I am destroying them with the earth."}]}